  "title": "Termites as pests of groundnuts",
  "abstract": "Different kinds of damage to groundnuts from termites are described. In addition to causing significant losses in yield by direct attack termites may also cause damage that predisposes pods to invasion by toxigenic fungi. control measures are briefly indicated",
